lead_paragraph: Ashleigh Barty's short stint as a professional cricketer has helped the former Wimbledon junior champion refresh for the grind of the tennis tour, according to her cricket coach Andy Richards.

headline.print_headline: Multi-Talented Barty's Return to Court a Loss for Cricket
